OL,3,CResidents wait up to five years for
OL,4,Cparking permits
OL,6,FResidents in say they are facing a
OL,7,F"nightmare" wait of up to five years
OL,8,Ffor a permit.
OL,10,FBen Osmand applied back in 2019 and is
OL,11,Fstill on the list for one.
OL,13,FHe explained: "If you're like me and
OL,14,Fyou work late then you've got nowhere
OL,15,Fto park at night ... it's a nightmare."
OL,17,FResidents in also face lengthy waiting
OL,18,Flists.
