OL,6,FDan George said: "It's now coming up
OL,7,Fto 30 months and we haven't heard
OL,8,Fanything back yet, it can be very
OL,9,Ffrustrating."
OL,11,FSt Helier Constable Simon Crowcroft
OL,12,Ftold ITV News: "The fact is that
OL,13,Fdemand far outstrips supply many times
OL,14,Fover.
OL,16,F"There are far more people wanting a
OL,17,Fresident's parking permit than there
OL,18,Fare spaces."
