OL,6,FComplaints have also been made about
OL,7,Fthe rising cost of parking schemes in
OL,8,Fboth parishes.
OL,10,FThe average permit in St Saviour will
OL,11,Fset residents back #900 a year, while
OL,12,Fthree out of the four parking zones in
OL,13,FSt Helier cost more than #400 for a 12-
OL,14,Fmonth permit.
OL,16,FConstable Crowcroft added: "Clearly
OL,17,Fpeople on the scheme don't like to see
OL,18,Fthe costs going up, it's gone up with
OL,19,Finflation this year.
