OL,6,F"But, it's still much much cheaper
OL,7,Fthan the alternative which is a season
OL,8,Fticket at a car park or to rent a
OL,9,Fprivate parking space."
OL,11,FSome are having to spend thousands of
OL,12,Fpounds on private parking instead.
OL,14,FHe believes pressure on the system has
OL,15,Fbeen exacerbated by residents in new
OL,16,Fhousing developments applying for
OL,17,Fpermits as their properties do not
OL,18,Fhave a parking space.
