OL,6,FIn St Helier, there is a review into
OL,7,Fthe lack of parking which Constable
OL,8,FCrowcroft hopes will free up some
OL,9,Fspaces.
OL,11,FHe said: "We suspect there are some
OL,12,Fpeople who get a residents parking
OL,13,Fpermit and they simply store their
OL,14,Fvehicle in the street for the whole
OL,15,Fyear and they never drive it.
OL,17,F"That's not what the resident's
OL,18,Fparking scheme was designed to do,
OL,19,Fit's supposed to provide flexibility
OL,20,Ffor busy families."
